scenes.description: Mori Calliope introduces her guests, IRyS and Hakos Baelz, to the audience.
IRyS introduces herself as the Seiso Nephilim and jokes about her role in the "Wheel of Fortune" card set.
Hakos Baelz introduces herself as Chaos, the "doomsday rat," in a theatrical manner.
The trio discusses the concept of the Wheel of Fortune, comparing it to a gacha system.
Calliope explains she chose them for the Wheel of Fortune theme because she feels fortunate to have met them.
They reflect on their performance together, with Calliope praising how their personalities shone through.
IRyS and Baelz make a playful exit from the stage after a countdown.
Mori Calliope transitions to the merchandise introduction segment for her birthday celebration.
